<h3 id="secondary-page-layout">Secondary page layout</h3>

<p>The most common layout on the site. Used for sub pages.</p>

<p>Located at <a href="https://github.com/18F/18f.gsa.gov/tree/master/_layouts/project-page.html">_layouts/project-page.html</a>, this is the template for creating new project pages as well as <a href="/site/styleguide/components/#project-cards">project cards</a> that show up at <a href="/site/what-we-deliver/">/what-we-deliver/</a>.</p>

